# **Inflation Effects and Future Work Insights**
ğŸ” **Executive Summary**  
This project combines datasets of inflation in Egypt with recent job and salary data to analyze the impact of inflation on livelihoods and identify the skills needed to thrive in this economic environment. By leveraging SQL databases and Tableau, we aim to provide actionable insights into the skills and jobs that will be most relevant in the future.

